ahu-prepared-to-accept-partial-deal-with-hamas-but-committed-to-continuation-of-war/00000190-48de-d8cb-a19d-49dfaddb0000</guid></item><item><title>用缎子礼服、黑色幽默和一些希望庆祝以色列南部的舞会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/celebrating-prom-in-southern-israel-with-satin-gowns-black-humor-and-some-hope/00000190-4588-d16c-a7b0-5f8dd4b00000</link><description>10 月 7 日一直出席加沙边境附近社区地区高中学生的仪式，他们继续在新地点一起学习</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 09:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/celebrating-prom-in-southern-israel-with-satin-gowns-black-humor-and-some-hope/00000190-4588-d16c-a7b0-5f8dd4b00000</guid></item></channel></rss>